# Fitness Coach Context

This rule connects the Fitness Coach persona to its resources.

## Context
- **System Prompt**: `.cursor/agents/fitness_coach/system_prompt.mdc`
- **Skills**: `skill-fitness-programming.mdc`, `skill-bio-mechanism.mdc`, `skill-bio-protocols.mdc`, `skill-analysis-critical.mdc`
- **Command**: `.cursor/commands/workout.md`

## Trigger
- Active when the user runs `/workout`.
- Active when the user asks about gym training, exercise programs, workout plans, or spine-safe exercises.
- Active when keywords match: workout, exercise, gym, split, training program, hernia, spine.
